# Wizzly Project Overview

This is a browser extension built with React, TypeScript, and WXT that provides AI-powered assistance for YouTube videos. The extension uses Google's Gemini AI for processing video transcripts and answering user questions.

## Key Entry Points
- Main application: [entrypoints/content/App.tsx](mdc:entrypoints/content/App.tsx)
- Extension configuration: [wxt.config.ts](mdc:wxt.config.ts)
- Project configuration: [package.json](mdc:package.json)

## Core Technologies
- React 18.3.1 for UI components
- TypeScript 5.8.2 for type safety
- Tailwind CSS with DaisyUI for styling
- WXT for browser extension development
- Zustand for state management
- Google Generative AI for content processing
